---
title: Zucchini & Smoky Bean Quesadillas with Lime Sour Cream and Romaine Salad
description: Crisp flour tortillas are stuffed with black beans, sautéed onions and zucchini. Gooey, melted mozzarella ties everything together, and a crisp side salad cools it all down.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/zucchini-smoky-bean-quesadillas-f6aa5fbd.jpg
